thread.title_full: Ticketebo reviewed by Jody Wilson (Yarra Valley Rodeo)

author: Jody Wilson (Yarra Valley Rodeo)
title: Jody Wilson (Yarra Valley Rodeo)
text:
Oliver Hinton is a legend ! He and the ticketebo team were extremely helpful on advising me on our ticket selling system from start to finish. Also did an amazing job at the front gate on the night ,what a smooth entry for patrons. I would highly recommend ticketebo for any event
Jody wilson Yarra Valley Rodeo
